skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cannabis world
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Cannabis World will advise you on where cannabis is legal for medicinal or recreational use, or for cultivation. The global cannabis marketplace is daunting. Frequent enhancements to laws and regulations make it difficult to keep up. If you’re a continental traveler looking for information for a getaway, a global minded individual, or just curious, visit Cannabis World.
You can say:
"Alexa, open Cannabis World"
"Alexa, start Cannabis World"
